column33: Henry J. Bruman Map Collection
column43: The Henry J. Bruman Map Collection at UCLA contains historical and contemporary maps from around the world.  The digital collection focuses on historical maps of California, Los Angeles County, and the city of Los Angeles with an emphasis on maps from 1860-1950.  This is an ongoing project and maps will be added to this collection as they are scanned and processed.
